config ZMK_BEHAVIOR_EC_MSC
    bool "EC11 encoder single-shot mouse scroll behavior"
    default y
    depends on ZMK_MOUSE
    help
      Enables the ec_msc behavior which sends a single HID scroll event
      (press + immediate release) per encoder notch.  Unlike the stock
      ZMK scroll behavior, it never leaves a "stuck" release pending if
      a sensor event is lost mid-flight.
